  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegetable broth in a large pot until it simmers.",
    "Add soy sauce, tamarind paste, sliced shiitake mushrooms, star anise, ginger, and a pinch of sugar; let the aromatics infuse for 5 minutes, creating wok‑hei.",
    "Stir in sliced bok choy and cook until just wilted, about 2 minutes.",
    "Add rice noodles and simmer until tender, about 3 minutes.",
    "During the last minute, add fresh bean sprouts and stir in shredded stilton cheese until it melts into the broth.",
    "Turn off the heat, ladle the pho into bowls, and garnish with lime wedges and chopped cilantro."
  ],
